metadata.name: Wuwei
metadata.description:
"Wuwei‚Äù is a beautiful and serene collaborative artwork by Georgina and  Yuma, which seamlessly blends elements of nature, including a natural  landscape, flowing water, creating a harmonious and balanced  composition.

Inspired by the Taoist concept of non-action and  effortless action, it aims to evoke a sense of calm and inner peace,  while also suggesting the potential for effective action that arises  from aligning oneself with the natural flow of the universe.
